パッケージ analysis

クラス ClassFileVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • analysis.ClassFileVisitor
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.nio.file.FileVisitor<java.nio.file.Path>
    public class ClassFileVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.nio.file.FileVisitor<java.nio.file.Path>
    For visiting all class files recursively and create ClassNode of each class file.
    After creating an instance of this class, call Files.walkFileTree(java.nio.file.Path, java.util.Set<java.nio.file.FileVisitOption>, int, java.nio.file.FileVisitor<? super java.nio.file.Path>) with the instance as one of its arguments.

    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • ClassFileVisitor

        public ClassFileVisitor​(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​org.objectweb.asm.tree.ClassNode> classNodes,
                        int offset)
        パラメータ:
        classNodes - HashMap which will contain ClassNodes of all class files
        offset - offset to remove first several letters from the full paths of class files (eg. when setting 4 offset, "bin\src\Test.class" to "src\Test.class")
